          "These are recomendations, not mandates."
        ],
        [
          "Protect your face. It's been your greatest weapon time and time again. Use it, but care for it, and make certain NOTHING happens to it."
        ],
        [
          "You've taken the typical path of Thaumaturgy nearly as far as you can. Perhaps  you should look into Mastery of the Elements? Seems both Flashy and Useful."
        ],
        [
          "Play up your brainlessness. Your lightheartedness. Your ditziness and your Cowardice, Then Capitalize and Punish those who fall for it"
        ],
        [
          "Regency. Plain and Simple. It will be yours."
